Breakthrough skin care products made with effective, naturally derived ingredients is Anaiti's specialty. Its Advanced Line and Wrinkle Smoothing Cream for Celebrity Skin is formulated with three of today's most effective anti-aging, anti-wrinkle components. Powerful humectant Hyaluronic Acid is one of the best moisturizers on the market, working on all skin types to create smooth, supple and hydrated skin. Complementing Hyaluronic Acid is Argireline, the clinically proven peptide that reduces wrinkles by 30 percent. Argireline, or acetyl hexapeptide-3, inhibits facial muscle neurotransmitters, relaxing the face, smoothing out fine lines and wrinkles and creating a safe, compelling alternative to Botox. The final powerhouse ingredient, Matrixyl, nearly doubles the skin's production of collagen, improving elasticity, firmness and plumpness. Often lauded as one of the best day creams available, Advanced Line and Wrinkle Smoothing Cream is cruelty-free, made only at certified facilities in Canada and contains absolutely no paraben.

*Vitamin C is key to the production of collagen, a protein that aids in the growth of cells and blood vessels and gives skin its firmness and strength. Vitamin C also helps create scar tissue and ligaments, slows the rate of free-radical damage, and helps your skin repair itself. *Shea butter helps to improve skin tone and elasticity while moisturizing to help skin appear smoother, making wrinkling less noticeable. *Glycerin is a known humectant in cosmetics and personal care products. It has the ability to attract or draw water from air which helps maintain the skin's water balance on an intercellular level. *Retinol Palmitate a derivative of vitamin A, reduces the appearance of fine lines and deep wrinkles to improve the look of collagen-depleted skin, while complementing the skin's natural process to reduce the appearance of pore size. *Marine collagen is a botanical ingredient that replenishes the connective tissue supporting the skin structure and works to deeply hydrate skin for healthy, resilient skin cells. *Resveratrol is a naturally-occurring polyphenols antioxidant that is found in some plant products like grapes and cocoa and defend against rough environments like excessive ultraviolet light, infections and climate changes.
